<module>
    <h>obair</h>
    <p><g>obair</g>
        <fem/>
        <en>working, work</en></p>

    <section>
        <h>subjects</h>
        <section id="sbjs-people">
            <h>people</h>
            <p>Examples with proper nouns – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri <a href="?gd=ag">ag</a> obair.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary is working</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Calum <a href="?gd=ag">ag</a> obair.</gd>
                        <tr>Malcolm is working</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with conjoined subjects – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri agus Calum <a href="?gd=ag">ag</a> obair.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary and Malcolm are working</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri agus Calum ag obair anns an achadh an diugh.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary and Malcolm are working in the field today.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6–7</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p><g><a href="?gd=clachair">clachair</a> [ag] obair</g>
                <en>a mason working</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>An robh an clachair ag obair air a’ bhalla fad an latha an dé? Bha.</gd>
                        <tr>Was the mason working on the wall all day yesterday? Yes, he was.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>

            <p><g><a href="?gd=saor^n">saor</a> [ag] obair</g>
                <en>a carpenter working</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha an saor trang ag obair air an taigh.</gd>
                        <tr>The joiner is busy working on the house.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 65</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>

            <p><g><a href="?gd=tuathanach">tuathanach</a> [ag] obair</g>
                <en>a farmer working</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Bha na tuathanaich ag obair gu trang anns an achadh an dé.</gd>
                        <tr>The farmers were working busily in the field yesterday.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 75</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>

            <p><g><a href="?gd=maathair">màthair</a> [ag] obair</g>
                <en>a mother working</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Dh’éirich athair na cloinne agus màthair na cloinne aig sia uairean sa’
                            mhadainn. Thòisich am màthair air obair an taighe aig fichead mionaid an
                            déidh sia, agus chaidh an athair a mach a bhiadhadh a’ chrùidh aig
                            leth-uair an déidh sia.</gd>
                        <tr>The children’s father and mother rose at six o’ clock in the morning.
                            Their mother started on the housework at twenty minutes past six, and
                            their father went out to feed the cattle at half past six.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 183</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>

    <section id="objs">
        <h>pseudo-objects</h>
        <p><g>obair air <a href="?gd=balla">balla</a></g>
            <en>working on a wall</en> – <xl>
                <li>
                    <gd>An robh an clachair ag obair air a’ bhalla fad an latha an dé? Bha.</gd>
                    <tr>Was the mason working on the wall all day yesterday? Yes, he was.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                </li>
            </xl>
        </p>
    </section>

    <section id="locatives">
        <h>locatives</h>
        <p><g>obair ann an <a href="?gd=achadh">achadh</a></g>
            <en>working in a field</en> – <xl>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha Màiri agus Calum ag obair anns an achadh an diugh.</gd>
                    <tr>Mary and Malcolm are working in the field today.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 6–7</ref>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>An robh Màiri agus Calum ag obair anns an achadh? Bha.</gd>
                    <tr>Were Mary and Malcolm working in the field? Yes, they were.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 6–7 [adapted]</ref>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha Seumas sgìth: tha e ag obair gu trang anns an achadh.</gd>
                    <tr>James is tired: he is working busily in the field.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 7 [adapted]</ref>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha Seònaid sgìth ag obair anns an achadh.</gd>
                    <tr>Janet is tired working in the field.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 7 [adapted]</ref>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>Bha na tuathanaich ag obair gu trang anns an achadh an dé.</gd>
                    <tr>The farmers were working busily in the field yesterday.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 75</ref>
                </li>
            </xl>
        </p>
        <p><g>obair <a href="?gd=an_diugh">an diugh</a></g>
            <en>working today</en> – <xl>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha Màiri agus Calum ag obair anns an achadh an diugh.</gd>
                    <tr>Mary and Malcolm are working in the field today.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 6–7</ref>
                </li>
            </xl>
        </p>

        <p><g>obair <a href="?gd=taigh">thighe</a></g>
            <en>housework</en> – <xl>
                <li>
                    <gd>Dh’éirich athair na cloinne agus màthair na cloinne aig sia uairean sa’
                        mhadainn. Thòisich am màthair air obair an taighe aig fichead mionaid an
                        déidh sia, agus chaidh an athair a mach a bhiadhadh a’ chrùidh aig leth-uair
                        an déidh sia.</gd>
                    <tr>The children’s father and mother rose at six o’ clock in the morning. Their
                        mother started on the housework at twenty minutes past six, and their father
                        went out to feed the cattle at half past six.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 183</ref>
                </li>
            </xl>
        </p>
    </section>
